    tokens = re.findall(r'\w+', text)

    return word_freq

    counter = Counter(words)
    stopword_counter = Counter()

            stopword_counter[word] += 1

# remove the url in the text
    text = re.sub(r"https?://\S+", "", text)

    # split the text to words, remove the punctuation
    text = re.sub(r"[\W]", " ", text)

    # convert words to lower case and split
    words = text.lower().split()

    # count each word
    counts = Counter(words)

    # filter stop words and sort by frequency
    stop_words = [word for word, count in counts.items() if word in PREDEFINED_STOPWORDS]
    return sorted(stop_words, key=lambda x: counts[x], reverse=True)
